question: How much revenue does the payer UnitedHealthcare generate?
answers:
PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

SELECT (SUM(xsd:float(?totalClaimAmount)) - SUM(xsd:float(?uncoveredAmount))) AS ?totalRevenue
WHERE { 
  ?claim syn:payer ?payer .
  ?payer rdfs:label ?payerName .
  ?claim syn:totalClaimCost ?totalClaimAmount .
  ?payer syn:uncoveredEncounters ?uncoveredEncounters .
  ?payer syn:uncoveredImmunizations ?uncoveredImmunizations .
  ?payer syn:uncoveredMedications ?uncoveredMedications .
  ?payer syn:uncoveredProcedures ?uncoveredProcedures .
  BIND (xsd:float(?uncoveredEncounters) * xsd:integer(250)) AS ?uncoveredEncountersAmount .
  BIND (xsd:float(?uncoveredImmunizations) * xsd:integer(150)) AS ?uncoveredImmunizationsAmount .
  BIND (xsd:float(?uncoveredMedications) * xsd:integer(100)) AS ?uncoveredMedicationsAmount .
  BIND (xsd:float(?uncoveredProcedures) * xsd:integer(1500)) AS ?uncoveredProceduresAmount .
  BIND ((?uncoveredEncountersAmount + ?uncoveredImmunizationsAmount + ?uncoveredMedicationsAmount + ?uncoveredProceduresAmount) AS ?uncoveredAmount)
  FILTER regex(?payerName, "UnitedHealthcare") 
}

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral>
SELECT ?startMonth ?endMonth WHERE {
  ?payer rdf:type syn:Payer .
  ?payer syn:id "a735bf55-83e9-331a-899d-a82a60b9f60c"^^uuid: .
  ?payerTransition syn:payer ?payer .
  ?payerTransition syn:startYear ?startYear .
  ?payerTransition syn:endYear ?endYear .
  BIND (xsd:date(?endYear, ?startMonth, 1) - xsd:date(?startYear, ?startMonth, 1)) AS ?yearsMonths)
  BIND (xsd:integer(STRBEFORE(STR(?yearsMonths), "T")) AS ?years)
  BIND (xsd:integer(STR(SUBSTRING(STR(?yearsMonths), 6, 2))) AS ?months)
  BIND (xsd:integer(?months) + (?years * 12) AS ?totalMonths)
}
